snippet.title: Judge Dredd gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Judge Dredd, Dos PC game produced by Acclaim in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/judge-dredd/14453/
I played through a couple of levels of this slick movie tie-in, bashing perps and cracking down doors.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
